    <p class="text-muted lead mb-4">
      Schlaumeise connects biology, computer science, and acoustics to inspire students (Grades 1–12) to explore the world of local birds while learning the foundations of Artificial Intelligence.
    </p>
    <div class="row g-4 mt-2">
      <div class="col-md-11">
        <p class="text-muted">
          As a PhD research project at <strong>TU Chemnitz (Media Informatics)</strong>, Schlaumeise turns scientific research into exciting classroom experiences. Students learn to use technology not just as a tool, but as a window into the ecosystem.
        </p>
