        <h2 class="h5 fw-bold mb-3">Research Questions for Students</h2>
        <ul class="text-muted small">
            <li>What makes a Blue Jay's call different from a Robin's song?</li>
            <li>How does local noise pollution affect bird activity?</li>
            <li>Can we predict bird migration based on local sound recordings?</li>
        </ul>
